Package com.stuypulse.stuylib.network

Class NetworkTableWrapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.stuypulse.stuylib.network.NetworkTableWrapper
  • public class NetworkTableWrapper
extends java.lang.Object
    The NetworkTableWrapper is a very fast way to easily interface with a network table. If a function you want is not implemented, use getTable(), getRawEntry(), or getInstance() to call the function yourself
